  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Admitted at NICU in Seoul National University Hospital or Bundang Seoul National
             University hospital

          -  Infants who were diagnosed with PAH

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe allergic reaction to sildenafil

          -  Inotropics for hypotension within 3 days prior to enrollment

          -  AST or ALT &gt; 3x ULN

          -  Any condition that would make the participant, in the opinion of the investigator,
             unsuitable for the stud
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
